"Why is this in popular now?" Time to educate on how shallow the Popular Now feature is. 

It updates once a day around 7pm PST using some snapshot of in the moment views/favorite gain. Due to this realistically only the 30 (5 already popular now + 25) doujins on the front page around that time are eligible to make it into Popular Now as they are the ones with the highest gains in that moment due to being on the front page. 

If this site ever allowed user uploads you could pretty easily snipe Popular Now with almost any content.
